narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend the course if you need to fulfill the language requirement. Definitely try to get into Professor Valle's class.
A basic language class. Not much harder than level 2 Spanish.
I would definitely recommend this class to another student. In short, I would summarize this class as a great way to improve one's comprehension of Spanish.
